these days.

02:52.036 --> 02:53.670
<i>I answered
a personal ad</i>

02:53.672 --> 02:55.705
<i>in The New York Review
of Books.</i>

02:55.707 --> 02:57.741
<i>The celebrated writer
Mark Asprey</i>

02:57.743 --> 02:59.912
<i>was offering up his apartment
for a swap.</i>

03:02.013 --> 03:04.046
<i>He would have been
overwhelmed with responses</i>

03:04.048 --> 03:05.684
<i>if it weren't for the crisis.</i>

03:07.919 --> 03:09.653
<i>Instead, poor Mark ended up</i>

03:09.655 --> 03:11.791
<i>with my shithole
