03:13.625 --> 03:15.024
Well, fuck me.

03:15.026 --> 03:16.059
<i>And I got the keys</i>

03:16.061 --> 03:18.462
<i>to his inspiring
three-bedroom flat</i>

03:18.464 --> 03:20.163
<i>in the heart of London.</i>

03:20.165 --> 03:22.064
<i>Mr. Samson Young.</i>

03:22.066 --> 03:23.700
<i>Mr. Mark Asprey here.</i>

03:23.702 --> 03:24.835
<i>Checking in to see
