03:24.837 --> 03:26.035
<i>your plane trip, mate.</i>

03:26.037 --> 03:27.271
<i>Make yourself at home.</i>

03:27.273 --> 03:30.940
<i>Do feel free, by the way,
to touch everything.</i>

03:30.942 --> 03:33.075
<i>Everything in that place
