04:17.623 --> 04:18.954
<i>It's just going
to be delicious,</i>

04:18.957 --> 04:20.623
<i>and I can't thank you enough.</i>

04:20.625 --> 04:22.258
<i>Oh, I just hope
you enjoy yourself.</i>

04:22.260 --> 04:23.495
Hey, tiger.

04:24.630 --> 04:25.895
<i>Oh, yes.</i>

04:25.897 --> 04:29.000
<i>I do hope you get a chance
