04:58.796 --> 05:00.830
<i>well, where do you go?</i>

05:00.832 --> 05:02.832
<i>You go to a London pub.</i>

05:02.834 --> 05:04.700
Oi!

05:04.702 --> 05:08.037
Here he is. Samson Young.

05:08.039 --> 05:11.007
My famous American friend.

05:11.009 --> 05:14.010
